Package: tidyXCMS
Title: Tidy Interface for XCMS Metabolomics Data Processing
Version: 0.99.11
Authors@R:
    person("Jan", "Stanstrup", , "stanstrup@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0541-7369"))
Description: Provides a tidy interface for working with XCMS metabolomics data.
    This package offers functions to extract and manipulate XCMS peak detection
    and feature grouping results in long-format tibbles, facilitating downstream
    analysis and visualization.
